<chapter id="chap-Navigating_the_CloudForms_Management_Engine_Console">
	<title>Navigating the CloudForms Management Engine Console</title> 
	<para>
		The CloudForms Management Engine Console is a web interface used to manage your virtual environment. It is highly customizable and allows easy access to your management tasks.
	</para>
	<note>
		<para>
			While the appliance is starting, you cannot log in to the console. The console retries the connection every 10 seconds until all workers and processes have started.
		</para>
	</note>
